snippet.title: Dear Hearders! About fandom wars, Johnny Depp + Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Hey everyone! In this video I'm going to give my opinion about certain topics that have more and more uproared.
Specifically this is both for Deppheads and Hearders, aka Johnny Depp and Amber Heard fans.

I will speak of what I feel like about the newly come out audio files, about fandom hating and about fandom behaviour in general.
And yes, this video will be hard to make, since it's a live, I have not written myself a script, and I just try to word my thoughts as good as possible. (Keep in mind, English is NOT my mother language).

Feel free to discuss (NOT FIGHT) in the comments down below, add thoughts and so on, and if you want, hit the subscribe button for more in the future💚🔥

My Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/insanitired/

My Twitter:
https://twitter.com/Insanitired?s=09
